Package: reSense
Type: Package
Title: A package to make basic Remote Sensing in R easy.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Pedro Blaya Luz
Maintainer: Pedro Blaya Luz <blaya.luz@gmail.com>
Description: This package contains functions for easily gathering 
    multispectral imaging and vegetation indices from Google Earth Engine.
    Under development, currently only functions for gathering
    Landsat-8 images and indices are included.
License: What license is it under?
